Class FormsetUrlConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.aemds.formset.constants.FormsetUrlConstants

  • public class FormsetUrlConstants
extends Object
    The class holds the constants for request parameters/ request selectors that are passed to the FormsetServlet/FormsetSubmitServlet
